<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">Master of Darkness</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The game's intro has Ferdinand Social receive a message to go Thames River and beware of Dracula via ouija board.	</p>
